attributes.Long form description: The student is building a table. The student starts by inspecting it, then assembling the legs on the shelf. The student uses an allen wrench to screw in the screws, first the first two, then the next two, then the third two, and so on until all the legs are attached. The student then rotates the table clockwise and screws in the final three screws. Finally, the student places the table.
